# Inventory Quantum: Complete Transfer Document

> **Advanced Inventory Optimization with Deep Learning, Quantum Computing, and Reinforcement Learning**

---

## 🎯 Project Overview

**Inventory Quantum** is a research-grade, production-ready inventory optimization system demonstrating mastery of cutting-edge ML/AI techniques. Built as a full-stack application with FastAPI backend and modern web dashboard.

| Category | Technologies | Innovation Level |
|----------|--------------|------------------|
| **Deep Learning** | TFT, LightGBM, ARIMA | Google's SOTA architecture |
| **Quantum Computing** | QUBO, QAOA Simulation | True quantum algorithm |
| **Reinforcement Learning** | Conservative Q-Learning | Offline RL with OOD regularization |
| **Uncertainty** | Conformal Prediction | Distribution-free guarantees |
| **Advanced ML** | Meta-Learning, GNN, Causal | 14+ algorithms |
| **Infrastructure** | Docker, GitHub Actions, AWS | Production-ready |

---

