## 🧠 1. Deep Learning Forecasting

### 1.1 Temporal Fusion Transformer (TFT)
**File:** [tft.py](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/tft.py) | **481 lines**

Full implementation of Google's 2021 SOTA time series model:

| Component | Description | Mathematical Formulation |
|-----------|-------------|-------------------------|
| **Variable Selection Network (VSN)** | Learns feature importance | $v_t = \sum_{i=1}^{n} \alpha_i \cdot \text{GRN}(x_t^{(i)})$ |
| **Gated Residual Network (GRN)** | Core building block | $\text{GRN}(a, c) = \text{LayerNorm}(a + \text{GLU}(\eta_1) \odot \eta_2)$ |
| **Interpretable Multi-Head Attention** | Shared values for visualization | Attention patterns stored for analysis |
| **Quantile Regression** | Multi-horizon uncertainty | Configurable quantiles [0.1, 0.5, 0.9] |

**Classes:** [TFTConfig](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/tft.py#23-39), [GatedResidualNetwork](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/tft.py#41-99), [VariableSelectionNetwork](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/tft.py#101-141), [InterpretableMultiHeadAttention](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/tft.py#143-213), [TemporalFusionTransformer](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/tft.py#215-481)

