## ⚛️ 2. Quantum Computing

### 2.1 QUBO Optimization
**File:** [qubo.py](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qubo.py) | **296 lines**

**Quadratic Unconstrained Binary Optimization:**
$$\min_x x^T Q x$$

| Component | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Binary Encoding** | 8 bits = 256 quantity levels |
| **Holding Cost** | $Q_{ii} \propto h \cdot 2^i$ |
| **Ordering Cost** | Fixed penalty for positive orders |
| **Stockout Cost** | Penalty for service level violations |

**Class:** [QUBOOptimizer](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qubo.py#11-296) with methods: [_build_qubo_matrix()](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qubo.py#62-129), [_evaluate_solution()](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qubo.py#130-170), [optimize()](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qubo.py#171-235), [compare_solvers()](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qubo.py#236-296)

### 2.2 QAOA Simulation (True Quantum Algorithm)
**File:** [qaoa.py](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qaoa.py) | **361 lines**

**NOT just "quantum-inspired" - actual QAOA implementation:**

$$|\psi(\gamma, \beta)\rangle = U_M(\beta_p) U_C(\gamma_p) \cdots U_M(\beta_1) U_C(\gamma_1) |+\rangle^{\otimes n}$$

| Component | Mathematical Description |
|-----------|-------------------------|
| **Initial State** | $|+\rangle^{\otimes n} = (1/\sqrt{2^n}) \sum |x\rangle$ |
| **Cost Unitary** | $U_C(\gamma) = e^{-i\gamma C}$ |
| **Mixer Unitary** | $U_M(\beta) = e^{-i\beta B}$, $B = \sum X_i$ |
| **Expectation** | $\langle\psi(\gamma,\beta)|C|\psi(\gamma,\beta)\rangle$ |

**Classes:** [QAOAResult](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qaoa.py#18-27), [QAOASimulator](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qaoa.py#29-239), [HybridQuantumClassicalOptimizer](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qaoa.py#241-345), [QUBOWithQAOA](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/qaoa.py#347-361)

**Features:**
- Up to 12 qubits (2^12 = 4096 basis states)
- COBYLA variational optimization
- Comparison: QAOA vs SA vs Exact solver

### 2.3 Simulated Annealing
**File:** [simulated_annealing.py](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/decision/simulated_annealing.py) | **7,598 bytes**

