## 📊 4. Uncertainty Quantification

### 4.1 Conformal Prediction
**File:** [conformal.py](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/conformal.py) | **386 lines**

**Distribution-free coverage guarantee:**
$$P(Y_{n+1} \in C(X_{n+1})) \geq 1 - \alpha$$

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Split Conformal** | Calibration set for nonconformity scores |
| **CQR** | Conformalized Quantile Regression (Romano et al., 2019) |
| **Adaptive Conformal** | Handles distribution shift (Gibbs & Candès, 2021) |

**Classes:** [SplitConformalPredictor](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/conformal.py#32-113), [ConformilizedQuantileRegression](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/conformal.py#115-192), [AdaptiveConformalForecaster](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/conformal.py#194-259), [ConformalForecaster](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/forecasting/conformal.py#261-386)

