## 🔍 6. Monitoring & Drift Detection

### 6.1 Drift Detection
**File:** [drift.py](file:///d:/inventory-quantum-main/app/monitoring/drift.py) | **312 lines**

| Method | Threshold |
|--------|-----------|
| **PSI** | < 0.1: OK, 0.1-0.2: Moderate, > 0.2: Significant |
| **KS Test** | p-value based |
| **Jensen-Shannon** | Symmetric, bounded [0, 1] |

