## ✨ Top 10 Transfer Differentiators

1. **True Quantum Algorithm** - Actual QAOA simulation, not "quantum-inspired"
2. **SOTA Forecasting** - Full TFT with VSN, GRN, Interpretable MHA
3. **Distribution-Free Uncertainty** - Conformal prediction with coverage guarantees
4. **Offline RL** - CQL solving no-online-interaction constraint
5. **Statistical Rigor** - Friedman, Nemenyi, Bootstrap, Shapley
6. **Enterprise Integrations** - 13 platforms (Shopify, SAP, Amazon, etc.)
7. **Multi-Objective Optimization** - NSGA-II Pareto frontier
8. **Full-Stack Production** - Docker, CI/CD, AWS S3
9. **NeurIPS-Format Paper** - Academic-quality documentation
10. **14+ Advanced ML Algorithms** - Meta-Learning, GNN, Causal Inference, A/B Testing

